olive oil
1 packet ciabatta
1 cucumber
1 head cos lettuce
2 radish
1 packet pine nuts
1 packet capers
1 bottle Balsamic & Olive Oil Dressing
1 packet Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise
1 packet Akaroa Cold Smoked Salmon

• Slice ciabatta in half. Toast or grill to your liking, then tear into chunks. Drizzle with olive oil and season
• Roughly chop cucumber and lettuce
• Trim and thinly slice radish

• Heat a frying pan over medium-high heat. Toast pine nuts, tossing, until golden, 3-4 mins

• In a bowl, combine ciabatta, cucumber, lettuce, radish, capers and dressing. Season
• Plate up salad and top with salmon and pine nuts
• Serve with mayo